msgctxt "Talk_000"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Who are you?<2.pa> Some kind of traveler?\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Did you come to make that big bird up in\n"
"the sky stop bothering us?<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: text_size
#. 3: text_size
#. 4: sound
#. 5: text_size
#. 6: text_size
#. 7: sound
msgctxt "Talk_001"
msgid ""
"<1.so><2.te_si>Nooo!<3.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"If everything goes back to normal, Kheel\n"
"will make me go to singing practice.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so><5.te_si>I mean...I feel bad that Molli's dad, Mr. Harth, got\n"
"hurt, but...<6.te_si>\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>But I definitely know I don't want\n"
"to practice singing!"
msgstr ""

